Title: Daycare Director Agapanthus
Description:
Amella has told me about the incoming whelps and about the daycare. Did you know Agapanthus is a renowned whelptender? I heard he fought back demons while rearing whelps! 

If he's as amazing as they say, I have much to learn from him. I only just received my Calling, but I will help in any way I can.

The Little Scales Daycare is in Valdrakken. I will gather my things and meet you and Agapanthus there.
ObjectivesText: Meet Agapanthus at the Little Scales Daycare in Valdrakken.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Agapanthus at the Little Scales Daycare in Valdrakken.
